summary: VEHICLE REFUSED TO START.  IT WOULD TURN OVER JUST FINE BUT THE ENGINE REFUSED TO FIRE.  SPENT 2 DAYS TRYING TO  FIRE THE ENGINE.  HAD TO GET VEHICLE TOWED TO DEALER.  UPON ARRIVAL AT THE DEALERSHIP, THE ENGINE FIRED RIGHT UP.  THEY COULDN'T DUPLICATE THE PROBLEM & AFTER COMPLETING DIAGNOSTICS FOUND NO REASON FOR THE FAILURE.   *NLM
